{"tid":1916860,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"恒生衰到碌地 騰訊亦常有淚","createTime":"2020-03-09T06:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T12:38:24.000Z","uid":182001,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6270f145bd44526a8bc2b736531ab60dd5bc8747","tid":1916860,"uid":182001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"【獅子山下 2020】#識唱一齊唱 #N世無改股票歌 #跌一千點 #行山銀行<br />\n原曲：羅文 獅子山下<br />\n改詞：大B <br />\n<br />\n恒生衰到碌地 騰訊亦常有淚<br />\n我哋行山(恒生)，在獅子山下相遇上<br />\n股價是歡笑多於唏噓<br />\n<br />\n恒生都插緊水<br />\n捱價亦常有淚<br />\n既是同舟 在獅子山上碌落去<br />\n沽貨不想來面對<br />\n<br />\n放開 高追有點矛盾<br />\n百三 一起再追<br />\n同舟人 誓相隨<br />\n無畏更無懼<br />\n<br />\n同處宰割邊端  撈底可有心水<br />\n我哋On鳩 在沙士抗疫寫下那<br />\n股票拋低來面對"},{"pid":"b6b361646fc972f0ea8e13877bb0e8555381442b","tid":1916860,"uid":198536,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a42c7b296eec781cab545695acd70b82630854","tid":1916860,"uid":272652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"都唔錯"},{"pid":"98382c91296fae7c83e028f77c11f03b6ac558e9","tid":1916860,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:58:39.000Z","msg":"禾系米要笑嫁"},{"pid":"88788f792920b1e159dae88c00e8e4ab40217c87","tid":1916860,"uid":310324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恒生都插緊水<br />\n捱價亦常有淚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n恒生使你心碎/醉？"},{"pid":"efb7d8064a8c1ee19302d0c4fd2fe670ee20b33d","tid":1916860,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"恒指都插緊水<br />\n牛證亦常有淚？"},{"pid":"bf493e31d1c91417f388124df1167e0e28ab6668","tid":1916860,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"已是熊一 在獅子山上仆落去<br />\n出貨  拋空 無樂趣"},{"pid":"38720fee7e78dac945a3f0bdd564e172ae08a640","tid":1916860,"uid":18